# Repository-level .gitignore

# 1) Local glibc checkouts anywhere
**/glibc_repo/

# 2) Ignore PoC-RAG folder at repo root
**/PoC-RAG/

# 3) Ignore specific generated datasets
**/patched_dataset1.csv
**/Ollama-Tryout/10-PoC.csv

# 4) Python and macOS clutter
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]

# 5) Ignore general dotfiles (e.g., .DS_Store) but keep essential VCS/config
.*
!.gitignore
!.gitattributes
!.github/
!.vscode/